### ===== POSTS API =====

### 1. Get All Posts
GET http://localhost:3000/post

###

### 2. Get All Posts (Empty result initially)
GET http://localhost:3000/post

###

### 3. Add a New Post
POST http://localhost:3000/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first post",
  "senderId": "user123"
}

###

### 4. Add another post with different sender
POST http://localhost:3000/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Another Post",
  "content": "Content from another user",
  "senderId": "user456"
}

###

### 5. Add a third post with same sender as first
POST http://localhost:3000/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Second Post by User123",
  "content": "More content from user123",
  "senderId": "user123"
}

###

### 6. Get All Posts (after adding posts)
GET http://localhost:3000/post

###

### 7. Get Posts by Sender (replace senderId with actual sender ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/post?senderId=user123

###

### 8. Get a Post by ID (replace post_id with actual post ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/post/replace_with_post_id

###

### 9. Update a Post (replace post_id with actual post ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/post/replace_with_post_id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Post Title",
  "content": "Updated content",
  "senderId": "user123"
}

###

### 10. Delete a Post (replace post_id with actual post ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/post/replace_with_post_id

###

### ===== COMMENTS API =====

### 11. Get All Comments
GET http://localhost:3000/post-comment

###

### 12. Create a Comment on a Post (replace post_id with actual post ID)
POST http://localhost:3000/post-comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Great post!",
  "postId": "replace_with_post_id",
  "writerId": "user789"
}

###

### 13. Create another Comment
POST http://localhost:3000/post-comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I agree with this!",
  "postId": "replace_with_post_id",
  "writerId": "user999"
}

###

### 14. Get All Comments (after adding)
GET http://localhost:3000/post-comment

###

### 15. Get Comments by Post ID (replace post_id with actual post ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/post-comment?postId=replace_with_post_id

###

### 16. Get a Specific Comment by ID (replace comment_id with actual comment ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/post-comment/replace_with_comment_id

###

### 17. Update a Comment (replace comment_id with actual comment ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/post-comment/replace_with_comment_id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Updated comment text",
  "postId": "replace_with_post_id",
  "writerId": "user789"
}

###

### 18. Delete a Comment (replace comment_id with actual comment ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/post-comment/replace_with_comment_id

###


